OL,5, Three gambling firms owned by William  
OL,6, Hill are to pay penalties of #19.2m for
OL,7, failing to protect consumers and weak  
OL,8, anti-money laundering controls.        
OL,10,FThe record penalty comes after the     
OL,11,FGambling Commission found new customers
OL,12,Fwere able to bet large sums over short 
OL,13,Fperiods without proper checks.         
OL,15,FIn one case, a customer was allowed to 
OL,16,Fopen a new account and spend #23,000 in
OL,17,F20 minutes without any checks.         
OL,19,FThe commission "seriously considered"  
OL,20,Fsuspending William Hill's licence.     
